companyName: iShares Edge MSCI Min Vol USA
description:
The investment seeks the investment results of the MSCI USA Minimum Volatility (USD) Index.
 The fund will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities of the index and may invest up to 10% of its assets in certain futures, options and swap contracts, cash and cash equivalents. The index measures the performance of equity securities in the top 85% by market capitalization of equity securities listed on stock exchanges in the U.S. that, in the aggregate, have lower volatility relative to the broader U.S. equity market.
